<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
            <link href="https://unpkg.com/tailwindcss@latest/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link href="./style/output.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style/style.css">
    <title>My Coffee</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header id="header" class="fixed main-color flex w-full gap-3 items-start flex-1 p-4 justify-between  ">
        <a href="/" class="logo cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1 link a">
            <img class="max-w-10 h-10" src="./img/mycoffee.png" alt="logo">
            <h1 class="text-white h-7">My Coffee</h1>
        </a>
        <div id="links" class="links w-full  none flex justify-between flex-4  ">
            <ul id="ul" class="flex gap-3 pt-1.5  ">
                <li class="text-white a hover:pl-3.5">
                    <a href="/">Home</a>
                </li>
                <li id="joinus" class="text-white cursor-pointer  relative flex a hover:pl-3.5">
                    Join Us
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8  text-gray-800 dark:text-white transform translate-y-[-4px]" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m8 10 4 4 4-4"/>
                    </svg>

                    <div  id="joinlinks" class="hidden absolute w-52 h-52 main-color justify-between  flex-col top-12">
                        <a href="/profile" class="border-b-2 tshadow border-amber-50 p-4">Profile</a>
                        <a href="/signin" class="border-b-2 tshadow border-amber-50 p-4">sign in</a>
                        <a href="/signup" class="p-4 border-b-2 tshadow border-amber-50">sign up</a>

                    </div>
                </li >
                <li class="text-white a hover:pl-3.5">
                    <a href="/coffee">Coffee</a>
                </li>
                <li id="joinus2"  class="text-white flex relative cursor-pointer a hover:pl-3.5">
                    Products
                    <svg class="transform translate-y-[-4px] w-8 h-8 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m8 10 4 4 4-4"/>
                    </svg>

                    <div id="joinlinks2" class="hidden absolute w-52  main-color justify-between  flex-col top-12 ">

                        <% for(let i=0;i<3;i++){ %>
                        <a href="/product/<%= products[i]._id  %>" class= "tshadow border-b-2 border-amber-50 p-4"><%= products[i].name  %></a>
                        <% } %>
                        
                        <a href="/products" class="p-4 tshadow">All Products</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="text-white a hover:pl-3.5">
                    <a href="/about">About</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="search cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-3">
                <div>
                    <a href="/card/">
                        <svg class="w-[48px] h-[48px] text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1.5a1 1 0 0 1 .979.796L7.939 6H19a1 1 0 0 1 .979 1.204l-1.25 6a1 1 0 0 1-.979.796H9.605l.208 1H17a3 3 0 1 1-2.83 2h-2.34a3 3 0 1 1-4.009-1.76L5.686 5H5a1 1 0 0 1-1-1Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                        </svg>

                    </a>
                </div>
                <form action="/search/" method="GET" class=" flex gap-2 items-center ">
                    <input name="name" class="bg-white h-10 rounded-md outline-none pl-2
                    " type="text">
                    <div class="btn-search flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-md">
                        <button type="submit" class="cursor-pointer">SEARCH</button>
                        <span>
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-black " aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-.757l-.707-1.707.535-.536a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.414l-1.414-1.414a1 1 0 0 0-1.414 0l-.536.535L14 4.757V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-2a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v.757l-1.707.707-.536-.535a1 1 0 0 0-1.414 0L4.929 6.343a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l.536.536L4.757 10H4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h.757l.707 1.707-.535.536a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.414l1.414 1.414a1 1 0 0 0 1.414 0l.536-.535 1.707.707V20a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-.757l1.707-.708.536.536a1 1 0 0 0 1.414 0l1.414-1.414a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.414l-.535-.536.707-1.707H20a1 1 0 0 0 1-1Z"/>
                                <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6Z"/>
                                </svg>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </form>

            </div>


        </div>
            <div id="lines" class=" lgnone absolute right-2.5">
                <svg class=" w-[38px] h-[38px] text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18 6H6m12 4H6m12 4H6m12 4H6"/>
                </svg>

            </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-main pt-28">
            <h1 class="text-center  t-color text-5xl   ">My Coffee</h1>
            <h3 class="t-color pt-3.5 pl-3 text-3xl" >Coffee world in your hands.</h3>
            <img class="pt-3.5 w-full" src="/img/img1.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="p-8">
            <h1 class="text-center  t-color text-6xl  mt-9 ">Coffee is my world</h1>
            <h3 class="t-color pt-3.5 pl-3 text-2xl mt-9" >Many good health reasons to drink coffee.</h3>
            <hr class="h-0.5 m-5">
            <span class="text-start block text-xl t-color">Caffeine stimulates your nervous system, signaling fat cells to break down body fat.</span>
            <span class="block mt-9 text-start  text-xl t-color">Coffee appears to be protective against two types of cancer: liver and colorectal cancer.</span>
            <a href="/coffee" class="tshadow block w-60 cursor-pointer s text-2xl mt-9 bg-amber-300 p-2 rounded-xl">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
            <hr class="h-0.5">
            <div class="w-full text-center mt-7">
                <h1 class="text-5xl t-color">Last Products</h1>
                <div class="pl-40 pr-40 pt-11 pb-11 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3  gap-3 justify-center">
                    <% for(let i=0;i<products.length;i++){ %>
                    <div class=" a flex flex-col items-start w-fit">
                         
                            <img width="100%" src="<%= products[i].img  %>" alt="">

                        <div class="text-start pb-3 pl-3 ">
                            <span class="block text-4xl mt-3"><%= products[i].name  %></span>
                            <span class="block text-2xl mt-3"><%=products[i].description.length>20? products[i].description.substr(0,20):products[i].description  %></span>

                            <a href="/product/<%= products[i]._id  %>" class="block w-60 cursor-pointer s text-2xl mt-9 tshadow bg-amber-300 p-2 rounded-xl">Learn More</a>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-12 p-8 bg-main text-start">
            <span class="flex gap-2 text-xl mb-5 t-color">
                <svg class=" t-color w-6 h-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M2 12C2 6.477 6.477 2 12 2s10 4.477 10 10-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12Zm9.408-5.5a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h.01a1 1 0 1 0 0-2h-.01ZM10 10a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h1v3h-1a1 1 0 1 0 0 2h4a1 1 0 1 0 0-2h-1v-4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-2Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>

                An additional note</span>
            <span class="flex gap-2 text-xl mb-5 t-color">


              <div>
                <svg class="t-color w-[24px] h-[24px] text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M7.833 2c-.507 0-.98.216-1.318.576A1.92 1.92 0 0 0 6 3.89V21a1 1 0 0 0 1.625.78L12 18.28l4.375 3.5A1 1 0 0 0 18 21V3.889c0-.481-.178-.954-.515-1.313A1.808 1.808 0 0 0 16.167 2H7.833Z"/>
                </svg>


              </div>
              When people think of coffee, they usually think of its ability to provide an energy boost. However, according to some research, it can also offer some other important health benefits, such as a lower risk of liver cancer, type 2 diabetes, and heart failure.
            </span>                
        </div>
    </main>
    <script
    src="main.js">
    
</script>
</body>

</html>